Undersized Weapons	KEY:Undersized Weapons ~ Lamia	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DESC:Although a lamia is Large, its upper torso is the same size as that of a Medium humanoid. As a result, lamias wield weapons as if they were one size category smaller than their actual size (Medium for most lamias).	BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Simple|TOHIT|3	BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Martial|TOHIT|3	BONUS:WEAPONPROF=TYPE.Exotic|TOHIT|3	BONUS:WIELDCATEGORY|ALL|1	SOURCEPAGE:p.186
Wisdom Drain		KEY:Wisdom Drain ~ Lamia		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DESC:A lamia drains 1d4 points of Wisdom each time it hits with its melee touch attack.																																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.186	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(1d4/touch)	BENEFIT:A lamia drains 1d4 points of Wisdom each time it hits with its melee touch attack. (Unlike with other kinds of ability drain attacks, a lamia does not heal any damage when it uses its Wisdom drain.) Lamias try to use this power early in an encounter to make foes more susceptible to charm monster and suggestion.

