Poison		KEY:Poison ~ Crag Linnorm		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatrual	DEFINE:PoisonDC|10+(HD/2)+CON																		DESC:Bite - Injury; Save Fort DC %1; Frequency 1/round for 10 rounds; Effect 2d6 fire damage and 1d4 Con drain; Cure 2 consecutive saves.|PoisonDC																			BONUS:VAR|PoisonDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Poison)				SOURCEPAGE:p.190	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(DC %1)|PoisonDC

