Poison		KEY:Poison ~ Ice Linnorm		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatrual	DEFINE:PoisonDC|10+(HD/2)+CON																		DESC:Bite--injury; save Fort DC %1; frequency 1/round for 10 rounds; effect 4d6 cold damage and 1d6 Con drain; cure 3 consecutive saves.|PoisonDC																					BONUS:VAR|PoisonDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Poison)				SOURCEPAGE:p.191	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(DC %1)|PoisonDC

